{# Base template for creative brainstorming - English version #}
Generate creative ideas for {{ topic }}:

CONTEXT:
- Genre: {{ genre }}
- Tone: {{ tone }}
{% if specific_context %}
- Additional context: {{ specific_context }}
{% endif %}

{% if constraints %}
CONSTRAINTS:
{% for constraint in constraints %}
- {{ constraint }}
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}

{% if avoid_elements %}
ELEMENTS TO AVOID:
{% for element in avoid_elements %}
- {{ element }}
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}

BRAINSTORMING REQUIREMENTS:
Generate {{ num_ideas | default(3) }} distinct creative ideas that:
1. Are original and engaging
2. Fit the {{ genre }} genre conventions
3. Match the {{ tone }} tone
4. Feel fresh and unexpected
5. Could enhance reader engagement

{% if idea_types %}
TYPES OF IDEAS TO GENERATE:
{% for type in idea_types %}
- {{ type }}
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}

For each idea, provide:
- A clear, concise title
- A detailed description (2-3 sentences)
- Why it would work well in this context
- Potential challenges or considerations
- How it enhances the story

{% if evaluation_criteria %}
EVALUATION CRITERIA:
Consider these factors when generating ideas:
{% for criterion in evaluation_criteria %}
- {{ criterion }}
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}

Be bold and creative while maintaining coherence with the established story elements.